Running the test:
1. Self test mode. 
    Prerequisites:
    * Python 2.7
    * Running MQTT broker on the localhost, port 1883
    
        python test.py
    
    The result should be OK

2. Test the esp8266-evb
    Prerequisites:
    * Python 2.7
    * Running MQTT broker

        export MQTT_RELAY=<relay topic>
        export MQTT_SENSOR=<sensor topic>
        export CLOUDMQTT_URL='mqtt://<user>:<pass>@<server>:<port>'
        python test.py
    
    The result should be OK
    
3. Do extensive test
   Execute in the bash:
   
    while [ 1 == 1 ]
    do
    python test.py
    sleep 1m
    done    
